response.original_title: Live at the Bourbon Room - Late Show
response.overview: Recorded live at the Bourbon Room in Hollywood, December 3, 2023, 8:30pm  Written and produced by Ben Acker and Ben Blacker  Starring the WorkJuice Players: Paul F. Tompkins, Paget Brewster, Joshua Malina, Janet Varney, Hal Lublin, Annie Savage, Craig Cackowski, Mark Gagliardi, and Marc Evan Jackson.  And special guest stars Keiko Agena and Sam Richardson.  Sparks Nevada, "Everyone Loops" written by Mickey Fisher  Captain Laserbeam, "Holiday Jeer" written by Liz Hara  Beyond Belief, "Dial Y for Yesterday" written by J. Holtham  Music by Jordan Katz and Jonathan Dinerstein.  Sound effects by Cayenne Chris Conroy.
response.title: Live at the Bourbon Room - Late Show
